sequenceDiagram
    participant App as AAOS App
    participant Backend as Car Pay-in Backend
    participant Redis as Redis
    participant DB as Car Pay-in DB

    Note over Backend,Redis: OAuth callback already saved vehicle list and temp app token

    loop Until login is complete
        App->>Backend: GET /auth/session/{session_id}/status
        Backend-->>App: Return pending or complete status
    end

    Backend-->>App: Return temp token and vehicle list
    App->>App: Select vehicle
    App->>Backend: POST /auth/confirm-car

    Backend->>Redis: Validate app_login_result:{session_id}
    Backend->>Backend: Verify selected car_id is in callback vehicle list
    Backend->>DB: UPSERT vehicles
    Backend->>DB: INSERT app_refresh_tokens
    Backend-->>App: Return final app tokens and vehicle confirmation complete
